 \{ ans_rule(5) \} to \{ ans_rule(5)\}  
$BR
b) $SPACE  The odds AGAINST E.
$BR
Answer: \{ ans_rule(5) \} to \{ ans_rule(5) \}
$PAR
END_TEXT

